OL,3,CMP calls for government to take over
OL,4,Crunning of Parc Prison following deaths
OL,6,FThe UK Government has faced calls to
OL,7,Ftake over the running of HMP Parc from
OL,8,Fprivate firm G4S, amid concerns over a
OL,9,Fspate of deaths.
OL,11,FNine adults have died at HMP Parc in
OL,12,FBridgend, South Wales, since the end
OL,13,Fof February, with four deaths so far
OL,14,Flinked to substance misuse and another
OL,15,Fpotentially so.
OL,17,FJustice minister Edward Argar argued
OL,18,Fthe contract "continues to perform
OL,19,Fwell" although he acknowledged there
OL,20,Fis "more to do".
