OL,3,CMP calls for government to take over
OL,4,Crunning of Parc Prison following deaths
OL,6,FG4S has managed the establishment
OL,7,Fsince it opened in 1997 and it
OL,8,Freceived a 10-year contract to
OL,9,Fcontinue operating it in 2022.
OL,11,FLabour MP Beth Winter (Cynon Valley)
OL,12,Ftold justice questions: "The most
OL,13,Frecent inspectorate of prisons report
OL,14,Finto HMP Parc in 2022 found that
OL,15,Falmost half of prisoners had easy
OL,16,Faccess to drugs and our current Welsh
OL,17,FAffairs Committee inquiry into prisons
OL,18,Fhas also received evidence regarding
OL,19,Fdrug use, as well the fact that Parc
OL,20,Fis both under-staffed and the staff
OL,21,Fare inexperienced."
