OL,6,FMs Winter pointed to this evidence,
OL,7,Frecent deaths and the recorded levels
OL,8,Fof violence in the prison, asking:
OL,9,F"Would the minister welcome a new
OL,10,Finspection of Parc by the chief
OL,11,Finspector?
OL,13,F"And given the #400 million cost of
OL,14,Fthe contract to G4S to run the prison,
OL,15,Fhas he given consideration to the
OL,16,Fprison service stepping in to manage
OL,17,Fit as it has done with Birmingham
OL,18,Fprison?"
