OL,6,FMr Argar said X-ray body scanners and
OL,7,Fhandheld devices are among the
OL,8,Fmeasures being rolled out to tackle
OL,9,Fdrugs at HMP Parc.
OL,11,FHe said: "Any inspection is a matter
OL,12,Ffor the chief inspector of prisons.
OL,14,F"In terms of the overall performance
OL,15,Fof Parc, I think it's important to
OL,16,Fremember that while there are
OL,17,Fchallenges that were addressed in the
OL,18,Furgent question (in the Commons)
OL,19,Fyesterday, Parc is a prison that is
OL,20,Frated as performing well and a
OL,21,Fcontract that is performing well.
