OL,6,F"I think in the 2022 inspection it got
OL,7,Fone measure of 'good' and three of
OL,8,F'reasonably good'. There is more to do
OL,9,Fand we will continue to work with the
OL,10,Fprison but the contract continues to
OL,11,Fperform well."
OL,13,FIn March, South Wales Police said it
OL,14,Fcould not confirm the four drug-
OL,15,Frelated deaths were connected to any
OL,16,Fspecific drug.
