OL,6,F"And at Wadsworth, a suspected
OL,7,Fterrorist escaped last year, the
OL,8,Fprison still isn't secure, and the
OL,9,Fgovernor has resigned. She's taken
OL,10,Fresponsibility ` when will he?"
OL,12,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk replied:
OL,13,F"So she's right that there are prisons
OL,14,Fwhere the standards are not where we
OL,15,Fwant them to be.
