OL,6,F"Take HMP Liverpool ` which I went to
OL,7,F` and in 2017 (Sir Robert Neill) will
OL,8,Fremember there was a scathing report `
OL,9,Fit has been turned around, it is safe,
OL,10,Fdecent, rehabilitative, prisoners are
OL,11,Fdoing excellent work.
OL,13,F"Take HMP Chelmsford, which had a
OL,14,F(urgent notification) and has been
OL,15,Fturned around.
OL,17,F"We take this incredibly seriously,
OL,18,Fbut we are the party that is investing
OL,19,Frecord amounts in our estate."
