OL,6,FAn HMP Parc spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fsafety of prisoners and staff is our
OL,8,Fnumber one priority, and our thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with the families and friends
OL,10,Fof those who have died recently at HMP
OL,11,FParc.
OL,13,F"The vast majority of our staff are
OL,14,Fhard-working and honest. As with every
OL,15,Fother prison in the country, we work
OL,16,Fclosely and effectively with the
OL,17,Fpolice and the HMPPS (HM Prison and
OL,18,FProbation Service) counter-corruption
OL,19,Fteam to crack down on the small number
OL,20,Fwho may break the rules.
