OL,3,CMP calls for government to take over
OL,4,Crunning of Parc Prison following deaths
OL,6,F"We use a range of tactics to tackle
OL,7,Fthe ingress of drugs and reduce
OL,8,Fdemand. This includes robust security
OL,9,Fmeasures for staff, visitors and
OL,10,Fprisoners as well as substance misuse
OL,11,Fsupport to those in our care.
OL,13,F"Tough sanctions are imposed on
OL,14,Fprisoners found to be involved in
OL,15,Fdrugs, including referral to the
OL,16,Fpolice for criminal investigation.
OL,17,FTargeted and random mandatory drug
OL,18,Ftesting is undertaken, as is the case
OL,19,Fin all prisons in England and Wales."
